Scenario

ABC Technologies wants to automate the deployment of a Java application. As a DevOps Engineer, your responsibility is to build a complete CI/CD pipeline using Git, Jenkins, Maven, and Docker.

You have been assigned to:

Develop a Java Maven application.
Store the code in GitHub.
Configure Jenkins to automatically build the project.
Package the application into a Docker image.
Deploy the application inside a Docker container.
Verify the deployment.
Update the application and redeploy automatically.
